(Zolm 23 zuloi 1906, bhaura-modhy prodex; mornnH 27 februvari 1931, olahabad-ut'tor prodex). Bharti-i svatontry-cholloullintolo ek krantivir addnamv tivari. Bapaichem namv pom. Sitaram' ani auychem namv zograni devi. Tachea bapaichi ddak vibhagantoli nokri komi pogarachi axil'lean to xikpakhatir bonarosak gelo. Thoim ek chhatronivasant tachi fukott veustha zali.

Bonarosak xikta astona, 1921 vorsa ddyuk ef vinddsoroche bhetticher bohixkar kheast zali. Ten'na mejisttrettan taka vichal'lem, ‘ tujem namv kidem ? ’ tannem thonddsannin zap dili- ‘ mhojem namv azhad. Mhojea bapaichem namv svadhin ani mhojem ghor asa bondkhonnit. ’ ten'na saun to brittix sorkarachea motan dohxotovadi tharlo.

Kaxi raxttri-i videapitthant xikta astona tachem purai lokx krantikarok cholloullinkodde axil'lem. 1925 chea kakori (lokhnovo) hangachea aggaddi uddoupachea kottant tannem vantto ghetlo. Kottantlea mukhel guneamvokarank dhorle punn chondroxekhor polisanchea hatank laglona. Soxstr kranti korpachea hetan tannem ‘ hindusthan ripblik ososiexon ’ he porne somsthechem ‘ hindusthan soxlistt ripblik ososiexon ’ hatunt rupkar kelo ani apnne svota he songhttonechem senapotipod apnnailem. He somsthecho lahor kott uktaddak ayil'lean ti somstha visrjit zali. Torikuy chondroxekhor azhad aplea soxstr krantichea dhyeyaposun mat'tuy fattim sorlona. Dil'lintlea peddhiuyole ani ponzab bonketole dorodde, sonddrs hea polis odhikareavelo hol'lo, kanpurak suru kel'lo gupt bambancho karkhano hea prokronnant chondroxekhoran sokri-i fuddakar ghetlo. Polisanchea hatak to kosoch lagna mhunn brittix sorkaran taka dhorun haddpakhatir 10 hozar rupeanchem inam' douril'lem. Dhoxttopuxtt kuddicho ani nigrohi vrit'ticho ho krantivir olahabad hangachea alfredd parkant polisankodden zal'le chokmokint jivitak ontorolo.

